before we charge forward.

07:34.788 --> 07:37.832
Get the monkeys off our backs.
Let's do this right.

07:37.958 --> 07:40.209
We should go on a date.
Okay.

07:40.293 --> 07:45.047
Get to know each other as these new people
not tied down by anyone.

07:45.132 --> 07:47.967
My place. I'll cook.

07:48.051 --> 07:50.302
I didn't know you could cook.

07:50.387 --> 07:53.889
There are so many things
you don't know about me,

07:53.974 --> 07:56.976
and I can't wait
to introduce them all to you.

07:58.228 --> 08:00.354
I'll see you later.

08:06.319 --> 08:09.071
You two should be wetting
yourselves with shame.

08:10.448 --> 08:12.366
Glee Club won sectionals,

08:12.450 --> 08:14.493
and you did nothing to stop it.

08:14.578 --> 08:19.331
If you were samurai and
my letter opener were sharp enough,

08:19.416 --> 08:22.751
I would ask you both right now
to commit seppuku.

08:22.836 --> 08:25.212
In Japanese, this means
ritual belly-slitting.

08:25.297 --> 08:27.798
We were seduced by the glitz
and glamour of showbiz.

08:27.883 --> 08:30.342
Let me drop some knowledge on you.

08:30.427 --> 08:33.012
Ever since Quinn Fabray got knocked up,

08:33.096 --> 08:35.514
I've been in the market
for a new head cheerleader.

08:35.599 --> 08:40.394
If you want the job
and back in my good graces,
you're gonna have to turn around...

08:40.478 --> 08:41.937
and listen up.

08:42.022 --> 08:44.982
You're familiar with a little Glee Clubber
named Rachel Berry.

08:45.066 --> 08:48.861
Rachel's the kind of girl
who wants things too badly.

08:48.945 --> 08:52.698
And what she really wants
is one Finn Hudson.

08:52.782 --> 08:55.409
I want you to go after him.
She'll go crazy.

08:55.493 --> 08:58.037
She won't be able to stand
you're dating him.

08:58.121 --> 09:00.080
Humiliated, shamed,

09:00.165 --> 09:02.416
