but to leave the group.

09:02.500 --> 09:06.629
And without her,
Schuester won't make it to regionals.

09:07.964 --> 09:10.674
- [School Bell Rings]
- [Will] I know it's been hard
on you since the baby drama.

09:10.800 --> 09:14.386
