You seem to be
handling it fine.

09:14.471 --> 09:18.641
Well, that's because I realized that I had
to find this new person inside of me,

09:18.725 --> 09:21.477
the one that was okay
with what happened.

09:21.561 --> 09:23.562
I just feel so bad about myself.

09:23.647 --> 09:26.398
