I can tell.
No, no, no. Emma.

25:31.989 --> 25:33.406
I understand.

25:35.075 --> 25:37.493
I'll pop in a movie.

25:37.578 --> 25:40.038
Do we have
to watch Armageddon again?

25:40.122 --> 25:43.208
Uh, it's that or BadBoys.

25:43.292 --> 25:45.335
They're the only DVDs
that Terri left behind.

25:45.419 --> 25:47.879
She liked to have Bruckheimer night
