when I'm with you.

26:11.570 --> 26:14.447
I'm glad you've come to that realization,
but you're too late.

26:14.531 --> 26:18.701
I've met someone else— a boy
who's finally worthy of my talent and love.

26:18.786 --> 26:20.745
Whoa, whoa, wait.

26:20.829 --> 26:23.539
Do I know him?
What, is he bigger than me?

26:23.624 --> 26:25.959
He doesn't go to this school,
and he's a senior.

26:26.043 --> 26:28.711
His name is Jesse,
and he's the male lead
in Vocal Adrenaline.

26:28.796 --> 26:31.422
We're both aware
that our Romeo-and-Juliet romance
will be a challenge,

26:31.507 --> 26:33.841
but our deep respect
for each other's talent
will carry us through.

26:33.926 --> 26:35.802
Rachel, don't you think
that's kind of suspicious?

26:35.928 --> 26:38.972
We make it to regionals,
and suddenly the top guy
in our main competition picks you up?

26:39.056 --> 26:42.267
I know it's hard to believe
that anyone would like me
without an ulterior motive,

26:42.351 --> 26:44.602
but you have to respect
that our love is real.

26:44.687 --> 26:48.022
Move on, Finn. I finally have.

26:55.531 --> 26:58.700
Mr. Schue. We have a problem.

27:03.414 --> 27:06.291
- Finn didn't fall for any of our tricks.
- Such as?

27:06.375 --> 27:10.128
I didn't wear a bra,
and I had them turn up the air conditioning.

27:11.505 --> 27:14.132
Ladies, I misjudged you.

27:14.216 --> 27:16.926
You may be two
of the stupidest teens
I've ever encountered.

27:17.052 --> 27:21.514
And that's saying something.
I once taught a cheerleading seminar
to a young Sarah Palin.

27:21.598 --> 27:25.727
Wait. We did find out Rachel's
with some dude
from Vocal Adrenaline.

27:25.853 --> 27:28.646
Name?
Jesse St. James.

27:28.731 --> 27:33.234
Ohh. Bringing down this club
may be easier than I thought.

27:33.319 --> 27:36.738
I'm engorged with venom and triumph.

27:37.906 --> 27:39.907
Now get the hell out of my office.

27:40.909 --> 27:43.453
